com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.exporter.server.rf1

Class SnomedSubsetMemberExporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.exporter.server.rf1.AbstractSnomedSubsetExporter
      • com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.exporter.server.rf1.SnomedSubsetMemberExporter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SnomedExporter, AutoCloseable, Iterable<String>, Iterator<String>

    public class SnomedSubsetMemberExporter
extends AbstractSnomedSubsetExporter
    Implementation of the SNOMED CT subset exporter. Supports RF1 output format. Used for simple type and language type reference sets.

    RR1 CSV header:

    • SUBSETID MEMBERID MEMBERSTATUS LINKEDID

    See Also:
    SnomedRf1Exporter, AbstractSnomedSubsetExporter, SnomedExportSetting
